-- Saakashvili Party Announces Primaries Before Georgia Vote
-- B y   H e l e n a   B e d w e l l
-- 2013-06-29T14:43:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-29/saakashvili-party-announces-primaries-before-georgia-vote.html
Georgian President Mikheil
Saakashvili’s party announced primaries today to choose his
successor from among four candidates ahead of presidential
elections in October.  • Saakashvili’s United National Movement will be challenged
by billionaire prime minister Bidzina Ivanishvili’s coalition.  • The four United National candidates include Davit
Bakradze, former parliament speaker, who is now leader of a
parliamentary minority group.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Helena Bedwell in Tbilisi at 
